quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  16,55,taakay jo ( naematain ) hum ne un ko ataa farmai hain un ki nashukri karen to ( mushrako ) duniya mein faiday utha loo . anqareeb tum ko ( is ka injaam ) maloom hojaye ga
  16,56,aur hamaray diye hue maal mein se aisi cheezon ka hissa muqarrar karte hain jin ko jantay hi nahi. ( kafroo ) khuda ki qasam ke jo tum iftira karte ho is ki tum se zaroor prssh hogi
  16,57,aur yeh log khuda ke liye to betiyan tajweez karte hain. ( aur ) woh un se pak hai aur apne liye ( betay ) jo Marghoob o dil pasand hain
  16,58,halaank jab un mein se kisi ko beti ( ke peda honay ) ki khabar millti hai to is ka munh ( gham ke sabab ) kala par jata hai aur ( is ke dil ko dekho to ) woh andohnak hojata hai
  16,59,aur is khabar bad se ( jo woh santa hai ) logon se chupta phirta hai ( aur sochta hai ) ke aaya zillat bardasht karkay larki ko zindah rehne day ya zameen mein garh day. dekho yeh jo tajweez karte hain bohat buri hai
  16,60,jo log akhirat par imaan nahi rakhtay un hi ke liye buri baatein ( Shayan ) hain. aur khuda ko sift aala ( Zaib deti hai ) aur woh ghalib hikmat wala hai
  16,61,aur agar khuda logon ko un ke zulm ke sabab pakarney lagey to aik jandaar ko zameen par nah chhorey lekin un ko aik waqt muqarrar taq mohlat diye jata hai. jab woh waqt ajata hai to aik gharri nah peechay reh satke hain nah agay barh satke hain
  16,62,aur yeh khuda ke liye aisi cheeze tajweez karte hain jin ko khud napasand karte hain aur zabaan se jhoot bikey jatay hain ke un ko ( qayamat ke din ) bhalai ( yani nijaat ) hogi. kuch shak nahi ke un ke liye ( dozakh ki ) aag ( tayyar ) hai aur yeh ( dozakh mein ) sab se agay beje jayen ge
  16,63,khuda ki qasam hum ne tum se pehli amton ki taraf bhi paighambar beje to shetan ne un ke kirdaar ( na shaista ) un ko aaraasta kar dukhaay to aaj bhi wohi un ka dost hai aur un ke liye azaab alim hai
  16,64,aur hum ne jo tum par kitaab nazil ki hai to is ke liye jis amar mein un logon ko ikhtilaaf hai tum is ka faisla kardo. aur ( yeh ) mominoun ke liye hadaayat aur rehmat hai
